---
import { SITE } from '../lib/site';
---
<section class="py-14 md:py-20">
  <div class="container-site grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 items-center">
    <div class="lg:col-span-6">
      <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-brand-800">About I Care Air Care</p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl md:text-4xl">Wesley Chapel's family-run HVAC team — since 2010</h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        We started I Care Air Care because the Tampa Bay HVAC industry had a problem: too many big contractors treating every call like a commission opportunity. sixteen years later we're a <strong>family-run team of {SITE.yearsInBusiness}-plus years</strong> — based on Foamflower Blvd in Wesley Chapel — known for one thing above all else: <strong>doing the right thing the first time</strong>.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        From a busted capacitor on a 95° afternoon to a full high-efficiency replacement with <a href="/financing/" class="text-brand-800 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-brand-800">financing</a>, our licensed technicians (Florida CAC1816515) show up in a marked truck, quote you flat-rate before any work begins, and back every job with a one-year repair warranty. It's the reason homeowners across <a href="/service-areas/wesley-chapel-ac-repair/" class="text-brand-800 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-brand-800">Wesley Chapel</a>, <a href="/service-areas/land-o-lakes-hvac-services/" class="text-brand-800 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-brand-800">Land O' Lakes</a>, New Tampa, Lutz and Zephyrhills have left us {SITE.rating.count}+ five-star reviews.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-7 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3">
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface p-4 text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-800">{SITE.customersServed}</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-600">Tampa Bay homes served</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface p-4 text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-800">{SITE.yearsInBusiness}+</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-600">Years in service</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface p-4 text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-800">{SITE.rating.count}+</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-600">5-star reviews</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface p-4 text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-800">1 yr</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-600">Repair warranty</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="lg:col-span-6">
      <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)]">
        <img src="/images/gen/ICAC%20Team%283%29-w600.webp"
             srcset="/images/gen/ICAC%20Team%283%29-w400.webp 400w, /images/gen/ICAC%20Team%283%29-w600.webp 600w"
             sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 580px, 100vw"
             alt="I Care Air Care service technicians in uniform ready for AC repair calls across Wesley Chapel, FL"
             class="w-full h-auto block" width="573" height="573" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
        <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4 rounded-lg bg-white/95 backdrop-blur ring-1 ring-slate-200 p-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent-500 text-white shrink-0">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2L2 7v10l10 5 10-5V7L12 2zm0 2.2L19.5 8 12 11.8 4.5 8 12 4.2z"/></svg>
          </span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-bold text-navy-700">Florida Licensed Contractor</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-600">CAC1816515 · Bonded · Insured</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
